name: eMusic Music Download File
summary: Learn about .EMP files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: eMusic files also use the .EMX extension depending on the version of eMusic Download Manager. Some versions of eMusic Download Manager are not compatible with EMP files. EMusic/J is compatible with both EMP and EMX files.
NOTE: EMP files do not contain actual audio data. They only contain the information necessary to download an audio file or a set of audio files.
